snippet.title: Marvel Rivals - PlayStation Closed Beta Announce Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Marvel Rivals, the Ultimate Super Hero Team-Based PVP Shooter, is now available to WISHLIST on PlayStation®5! 
Prepare for the Closed Beta Test, where players will assemble an All-star Marvel squad in epic battles across ever-changing battlegrounds.Wishlist now on PlayStation Store and get ready IGNITE THE BATTLE!

#MarvelRivals #MarvelGames #Marvel #ps5 #ps5games
